{"tid":303224,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"彭麗媛到訪劍…東華三院賽馬會松朗安老綜合中心","createTime":"2017-06-30T04:02:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-30T04:16:54.000Z","uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0b19db98f3096647e79692a49cff99bdd6f2424e","tid":303224,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T04:02:46.000Z","msg":"國家主席習近平與夫人彭麗媛訪港第二天，彭麗媛由特首夫人梁唐青儀陪同下探訪黃竹坑一家老人院，與長者及職員交流，當中彭麗媛跟長者進行互動，一同製作立體花。彭一行人逗留約半小時後離開，只在門口揮手，未有回應記者提問。<br />\n<br />\n彭麗媛約於10時40分到達香港黃竹坑南朗山道東華三院賽馬會松朗安老綜合中心，身穿白色套裝的梁唐青儀先行下車，與其他職員迎接身穿深色套裝配上灰色襟花的彭麗媛。逗留半小時後，彭麗媛在門外跟傳媒揮手，對於傳媒的提問，她只拱手作回應。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/1847324/%E5%BD%AD%E9%BA%97%E5%AA%9B%E8%A8%AA%E8%80%81%E4%BA%BA%E9%99%A2%20%E9%96%80%E5%A4%96%E6%8F%AE%E6%89%8B%E6%9C%AA%E5%9B%9E%E6%87%89%E6%8F%90%E5%95%8F\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F1847324%2F%25E5%25BD%25AD%25E9%25BA%2597%25E5%25AA%259B%25E8%25A8%25AA%25E8%2580%2581%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E9%2599%25A2%2520%25E9%2596%2580%25E5%25A4%2596%25E6%258F%25AE%25E6%2589%258B%25E6%259C%25AA%25E5%259B%259E%25E6%2587%2589%25E6%258F%2590%25E5%2595%258F&d=KtAiQ8SDkA72PzGucwi2MZZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=23b1aa7c\" target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/1847324/%E5%BD%AD%E9%BA%97%E5%AA%9B%E8%A8%AA%E8%80%81%E4%BA%BA%E9%99%A2%20%E9%96%80%E5%A4%96%E6%8F%AE%E6%89%8B%E6%9C%AA%E5%9B%9E%E6%87%89%E6%8F%90%E5%95%8F</a>"},{"pid":"78c9edd3b54cdada3a63bd6348ce557dc6d49b4c","tid":303224,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T04:04:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170303/photo/bkn-20170303132352164-0303_00822_001_02p.jpg?20170303135308\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170303%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170303132352164-0303_00822_001_02p.jpg%3F20170303135308&h=ae1096b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://www.tungwah.org.hk/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Photo-11.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.tungwah.org.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F08%2FPhoto-11.jpg&h=4768e68b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"391389a72cc1ffdcbfe532cb0e026c2010c11eb8","tid":303224,"uid":68547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T04:16:54.000Z","msg":"原來如此 難怪黃竹坑返工咁多警車"}]}